metadata.name: a KID Called BEAST
metadata.description: a KID called BEAST is a web3 brand and culture that starts with our digital collectibles. 10,000 of them, each unique and truly 3D, can be viewed in augmented reality and placed in any physical space. Each KID BEAST belongs to 1 of 20 beasthoods. The owner is given access to a sub-community of 500 like-minded individuals to innovate and prove which beasthood is alpha. Visit https://akidcalledbeasts.com for more details.
